"      &ldquo;Guidelines for the Diagnosis and Management of Asthma. NAEPP Expert Panel Report 3,&rdquo; August 2007, www.nhlbi.nih.gov/guidelines/asthma/asthgdln.pdf.",
"     </div>",
"    </li>",
"    <li>",
"     <div class=\"reference\">",
